      question: "A patient on enalapril (ACEi) and metoprolol (beta-blocker) is scheduled for surgery tomorrow. What is the medication plan?",
      options: ["Hold both medications", "Continue metoprolol (never stop beta-blockers perioperatively — rebound risk); hold enalapril on the morning of surgery (ACEi/ARBs cause refractory intraoperative hypotension)", "Continue both medications", "Hold metoprolol, continue enalapril"],
      correct: 1,
