      options: ["No special precautions needed", "This indicates HIGH risk for obstructive sleep apnea — bring CPAP to hospital, use continuous pulse oximetry postoperatively, minimize opioids using multimodal analgesia, and notify anesthesia of OSA risk", "Surgery should be cancelled", "Only nasal cannula oxygen is needed"],
